    <div class="- topic/body reference/refbody body refbody"><p class="- topic/shortdesc shortdesc">IBM StoredIQ is deployed as virtual appliances and is supported in VMware ESXi 5.0
        (all fix pack levels) or VMware ESXi 6.0 (all fix pack levels) environments. You must have a
        virtual infrastructure that meets the IBM StoredIQ hardware requirements.</p> 
        
        
        <section class="- topic/section section" audience="novice" id="unique_3_Connect_42_application_stack" nd:nd-id="application_stack" importance="low"><h3 class="- topic/title title sectiontitle" id="unique_3_Connect_42_app_stack" nd:nd-id="app_stack">Application stack</h3>
            
            
            <ul class="- topic/ul ul">
                <li class="- topic/li li">vCPU: 2</li>
                <li class="- topic/li li">Memory: 4 GB</li>
                <li class="- topic/li li">Storage:
                    <ul class="- topic/sl sl simple">
                        <li class="- topic/sli sli"> - Primary disk (vmdisk1): 21 GB</li>
