    <div class="- topic/body reference/refbody body refbody"><p class="- topic/shortdesc shortdesc">Before a deployment, verify that you meet these prerequisites.</p> 
        <section class="- topic/section section">
            <ul class="- topic/ul ul">
                <li class="- topic/li li">At least one physical server with sufficient processor, RAM, and hard disk configuration for the planned
                    management project.</li>
                <li class="- topic/li li">VMware ESX or ESXi on CD/DVD or USB drive.
                </li>
                <li class="- topic/li li">IP addresses, cables, and physical switch ports for at least the ESXi/ESX interface, one data server, one
                    gateway server, and one application stack.</li>
                <li class="- topic/li li">Network connectivity that is enabled from the following locations:
                    <ul class="- topic/sl sl simple">
                        <li class="- topic/sli sli">– The data server IP address to the gateway IP address on port 11103</li>
                        <li class="- topic/sli sli">– The gateway IP address to and from the application stack IP address on port 8765 and 5432</li>
