    </h1>
    <p class="- topic/shortdesc shortdesc">IBM StoredIQ is a virtual appliance that you deploy and configure in a VMWare virtual
        host environment.</p>
    <div class="- topic/prolog prolog">
        <div class="- topic/author author">Patrick Scully</div>
        <div class="- topic/copyright copyright">
